The villain Ling Chen has a history of hate and violence with the hero, Ye Zimu. Out of nowhere, a reset triggered Ling Chen to return to when he was 17 years old! He has a chance to stop the hero in his path, before Ye Zimu grows to become his worst enemy...
(Source: Bilibili Comics)

Beauty Queen, Idol, Hostess etc. Ryougoku Atsushi, a college student with the power to see the “Favor” in others, lives a comfy life supported by beautiful women. But one day, a girl calling herself his “childhood friend” appears, destroying his paradise. And maybe even his life… A harem suspense story, start!
